I"n<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>$ zip -r -s 5m myFiles.zip exampleFolder/
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-r</code> - is for recursive
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">-s</code> - splits the zip archive 
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">5m</code> - a specified size</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">myFolder.zip</code> - result name of the archive
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">exampleFolder/</code> - target folder</p>
